      "message": "We have 3 places where we can add modify displays:\n\n- The telnet console\n- The Extended Windows UI\n- The gRPC endpoint itself.\n\nCurrently the notification API will fire for any change coming from these. It sounds like you are looking for some sort of \"transaction\" where we accumulate a series of changes and apply them as a single operation (gRPC api mimics this).\n\nWe can do this, but it will make things more complicated.",
